text: KKSG-LP (103.7 FM) is a radio station licensed to Worland, Wyoming, United States. The station is currently owned by Sovereign Grace Bible Church. ==References== ==External links== * KKSG-LP Category:Religious radio stations in the United States KSG-LP Category:Radio stations established in 2015 Category:2015 establishments in Wyoming KSG-LP
